WHITENH= population that identifies as white only and non-Hispanic (P5);  
BLACKNH= population that identifies as black only and non-Hispanic (P5);  
AMINDNH= population that identifies as American Indian only and non-Hispanic (P5);  
ASIANNH= population that identifies as Asian/Asian-American only and non-Hispanic (P5);  
PACIFICNH= population that identifies as Pacific Islander only and non-Hispanic (P5);  
OTHERNH= population that identifies as other race and non-Hispanic (P5);  
MULTRACENH= population that identifies as multi-racial and non-Hispanic (P5);  
HISPPOP= population that identifies as Hispanic in combination with any race (P5);  
NOTHISPPOP= population that identifies as non-Hispanic (P5);   

HUTOTAL= total housing units (H1); 
HHTOTAL= total households, also number of occupied housing units (P21);  
POPINHH= population in households and not in GQ (P16); 
AVGHHSIZE= average household size (P16/P21);  
POPINGQ= population in group quarters (P29)
HOMEOWNPCT= share of households that own their housing (H4); 
OWNEROCC= owner households or owner-occupied units (H4); 
