POPOVER65= population age 65+ (P34); 
ERRORFLAG= quality control flag should be 0;
MEDIANAGE= median age for area (P13);
HH_UNDER18= housieholds with children ages 0-17 present (P20);
HH_65OVER= households with senior citizens ages 65+ present (P25);

CENSUS_SOURCE= Description of data source; 
YEAR= Year of data collection;
TCFLAG= Met Council-assigned code identifying location in the Met Council region (1), an adjacent MN county (2), or an adjacent WI county (3).
